title: Support Auto FasterTokenizer
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleNLP/pull/26 -->
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
New features
### PR changes
<!-- One of [ Models | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
APIs
### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
Support AutoFasterTokenizer. AutoFasterTokenizer supports **ErnieFasterTokenizer** and **BertFasterTokenizer** currently.
If user wants to use the tokenizer of faster version that AutoFasterTokenizer doesn't support, it will give warning and return the tokenizer of normal version.
### Usage

```python
from paddlenlp.transformers import AutoTokenizer

faster_tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained("ernie-1.0", use_faster=True)
tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained("ernie-1.0")

print(faster_tokenizer("I am playing football."))
print(tokenizer("I am playing football."))

print(type(faster_tokenizer)) # <class 'paddlenlp.transformers.ernie.tokenizer_faster.ErnieFasterTokenizer'>
print(type(tokenizer)) # <class 'paddlenlp.transformers.ernie.tokenizer.ErnieTokenizer'>

# AutoTokenizer doesn't support roberta_tokenizer, so return the normal version tokenizer
roberta_tokenizer = AutoTokenizer.from_pretrained("roberta-wwm-ext", use_faster=True)
print(type(roberta_tokenizer)) # <class 'paddlenlp.transformers.roberta.tokenizer.RobertaChineseTokenizer'> 

```

title: ErnieForGeneration加载训练后的模型报错
body:
欢迎您反馈PaddleNLP使用问题，非常感谢您对PaddleNLP的贡献！
在留下您的问题时，辛苦您同步提供如下信息：
- 版本、环境信息
1）PaddleNLP和PaddlePaddle版本：PaddleNLP 2.3.0rc0，PaddlePaddle 2.2.2.post101
2）系统环境：AI Studio V100 32GB 版本
- 复现信息：

0. 问题同 #1236

1. 使用ErnieForGeneration模型，可以进行训练。定义模型如下：

``` python
from paddlenlp.transformers import ErnieForGeneration

model = ErnieForGeneration.from_pretrained("ernie-1.0")
```

2. 训练完成后使用`model.save_pretrained(output_dir)`和`tokenizer.save_pretrained(output_dir)`保存模型参数与tokenizer的参数，文件夹内结果如下：

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/71769312/167164578-0779018c-a45c-45d3-84b1-d2a582915d9e.png)

3. 尝试加载模型和tokenizer的参数进行预测，加载代码如下：

``` python
from paddlenlp.transformers import ErnieTokenizer
```

### Compare:
```python
import torch
import paddle
torch.set_grad_enabled(False)
paddle.set_grad_enabled(False)
paddle.set_device('cpu')
from transformers import BertTokenizer
from roformer import RoFormerModel
from paddlenlp.transformers import RoFormerv2Model
text = [
    "人生的路丰富而漫长,就像在宇宙中穿梭。",
    "时而太空漫步,无拘无束;时而速度失控,遭遇窘境。这意味着，漫漫人生路，同时涌现着异彩纷呈和艰难险阻。",
    "不知不觉已然忙碌了半生，对人生这道深刻的命题，也有了层次不一的理解。",
    "十八岁：成长成人，前方有路",
]

pt_inputs = tokenizer(text, return_tensors="pt", padding=True, max_length=256)
pd_inputs = {k:paddle.to_tensor(v.numpy(), dtype="int64") for (k, v) in pt_inputs.items()}
```

Add RoFormerV2

### Reference:
- keras: https://github.com/ZhuiyiTechnology/roformer-v2
- pytorch: https://github.com/JunnYu/RoFormer_pytorch

### Compare:
```python
import torch
import paddle
torch.set_grad_enabled(False)
paddle.set_grad_enabled(False)
paddle.set_device('cpu')
from transformers import BertTokenizer
from roformer import RoFormerModel
from paddlenlp.transformers import RoFormerv2Model
text = [
    "人生的路丰富而漫长,就像在宇宙中穿梭。",
    "时而太空漫步,无拘无束;时而速度失控,遭遇窘境。这意味着，漫漫人生路，同时涌现着异彩纷呈和艰难险阻。",

]
tokenizer = BertTokenizer.from_pretrained("roformer_v2_chinese_char_base")
pt_inputs = tokenizer(text, return_tensors="pt", padding=True, max_length=256)
pd_inputs = {k:paddle.to_tensor(v.numpy(), dtype="int64") for (k, v) in pt_inputs.items()}
pt_model = RoFormerModel.from_pretrained("roformer_v2_chinese_char_base")
pt_model.eval()
pd_model = RoFormerv2Model.from_pretrained("roformer_v2_chinese_char_base")

print("paddle vs pytorch")

print("max diff :", (pd_outputs - pt_outputs).abs().max())
# paddle vs pytorch
# mean diff : tensor(7.8678e-07)
# max diff : tensor(1.6212e-05)
```
### CovertCode
- download pytorch_model `wget https://huggingface.co/junnyu/roformer_v2_chinese_char_large/resolve/main/pytorch_model.bin`

```python
from collections import OrderedDict
import argparse

huggingface_to_paddle = {
    "embeddings.LayerNorm": "embeddings.norm",
    "encoder.layer": "encoder.layers",
    "attention.self.query": "self_attn.q_proj",
    "attention.self.key": "self_attn.k_proj",
    "attention.self.value": "self_attn.v_proj",
    "attention.output.dense": "self_attn.out_proj",
    "intermediate.dense": "linear1",
    "output.dense": "linear2",
    "attention.output.LayerNorm": "norm1",
    "output.LayerNorm": "norm2",
}


def convert_pytorch_checkpoint_to_paddle(pytorch_checkpoint_path,
                                         paddle_dump_path):

    import torch
    import paddle
    pytorch_state_dict = torch.load(pytorch_checkpoint_path, map_location="cpu")
    paddle_state_dict = OrderedDict()
    for k, v in pytorch_state_dict.items():
        if "encoder.embed_positions." in k or "predictions.decoder.weight" in k:
            continue
        if k[-7:] == ".weight":
            if ".embeddings." not in k and ".LayerNorm." not in k:
                v = v.transpose(0, 1)
        oldk = k
        for huggingface_name, paddle_name in huggingface_to_paddle.items():
            k = k.replace(huggingface_name, paddle_name)

        k = k.replace("roformer", "roformerv2")

        print(f"Converting: {oldk} => {k}")
        paddle_state_dict[k] = v.data.numpy()

    paddle.save(paddle_state_dict, paddle_dump_path)


if __name__ == "__main__":
    parser = argparse.ArgumentParser()
    parser.add_argument(
        "--pytorch_checkpoint_path",
        default="./pytorch_model.bin",
        type=str,
        help="Path to the Pytorch checkpoint path.")
    parser.add_argument(
        "--paddle_dump_path",
        default="./model_state.pdparams",
        type=str,
        help="Path to the output Paddle model.")
    args = parser.parse_args()
    convert_pytorch_checkpoint_to_paddle(args.pytorch_checkpoint_path,
                                         args.paddle_dump_path)

```

title: AutoModel预测阶段必须使用model.eval才能保证同一输入有同一结果，与huggingface不一致，体验不好
body:
AutoModel预测阶段必须使用model.eval才能保证同一输入有同一结果，与huggingface不一致，体验不好

1）Paddle  2.2.1；PaddleNLP 2.2.3；
2）系统环境：Linux，python3.6.2
3）问题代码：
```python
    import paddle
    from paddlenlp.transformers import BertModel, BertTokenizer
    tokenizer = BertTokenizer.from_pretrained('bert-wwm-chinese')
    model = BertModel.from_pretrained('bert-wwm-chinese')
    inputs = tokenizer("欢迎使用百度飞桨!")
    inputs = {k:paddle.to_tensor([v]) for (k, v) in inputs.items()}
    # model.eval()  不使用这一行的话，下面的结果不一致
    output = model(**inputs)
    print(output[0])
    output = model(**inputs)
    print(output[0])
```
